 3sc. Photo: TWITTER/OFFICIAL3SC  Also, each of the team officials was promised a sum of N2 million and a plot of land, while the club chairman was similarly promised N3 million and a plot of land.
 
Elder Oyewole revealed that the team officials had made numerous efforts to ensure that the team got its rewards, but their efforts have been abortive. 
 
